  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Druid Domain Power</strong><br/><br/><p>At 8th level, you treat the penalties from natural or magical wind effects as two steps less severe. In addition, you are surrounded by a cushion of air that grants you a bonus equal to 1/2 your druid level on saving throws against gases, gaseous breath weapons, inhaled poisons, and similar effects.</p><p>Alternatively, you can choose to gain a Small air elemental as a familiar, as if you possessed the Improved Familiar feat. Your effective wizard level for this ability is equal to your druid level and stacks with other classes that grant a familiar.</p>",
